{"tid":48736,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"休班警，加一分","createTime":"2016-12-21T08:55:19.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-21T09:11:50.000Z","uid":3469,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"acca1b2c51b7e39a1c45502a4a11d11e2ecfebe7","tid":48736,"uid":3469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T08:55:19.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/breaking/20161221/56074659\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fbreaking%2F20161221%2F56074659&d=NztypxuZbm0QUhDvt%2FI62wv3KisNQlPySkJrDkY9tT8%3D&h=6493448c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fbreaking%2F20161221%2F56074659&h=1ce5bf35\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/breaking/20161221/56074659</a><br />\n<br />\n3名休班警涉嫌酒後在街頭與3名少女毆鬥，事後全部人被捕。事發於凌晨3時半左右，4名休班警員，在旺角夜店消遣後帶醉離開，至旺角道28號對開，疑與3名同為22歲的少女踫撞後，一名少女感覺被人觸摸臀部，大怒與其中3警爭執，雙方繼而大打出手，眾人均手部受傷。警方接報到場調查，以涉嫌在公眾地方打架將6人拘捕，全部人事後被送廣華醫院治理。<br />\n<br />\n被捕3名休班警員，分別為40歲姓游、33歲姓潘及31歲姓唐。據悉，他們3人為毒品調查科探員，其中一人為警長。案件交由旺角警區重案組跟進。警方表示，警隊非常重視人員的操守，任何人員干犯違法行為，警隊絕不容忍和姑息，定必嚴正處理，進行刑事調查及紀律覆檢。"},{"pid":"f52e45aa09226d4bae2189f7a85bf0e9915f0ebc","tid":48736,"uid":90,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T08:56:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0291e0f634130662b25350ffd7d3403aa1f8edd8","tid":48736,"uid":13835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T08:56:51.000Z","msg":"依家佢哋總分幾多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9a5542a2c6c2f9b2463adc702c2e4e9e1983f33","tid":48736,"uid":25350,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T09:07:43.000Z","msg":"慈母放咗工真係計時炸彈"},{"pid":"e14c6cc1eea0ec0f7e6330463dbf59ff6d5f3730","tid":48736,"uid